1
00:01:08,355 --> 00:01:09,065
It is said that

2
00:01:09,435 --> 00:01:12,105
you often went to the Second Prince's residence

3
00:01:13,015 --> 00:01:15,025
Was it for official business

4
00:01:16,685 --> 00:01:17,935
Or for private matters?

5
00:01:20,475 --> 00:01:23,645
Your Majesty, the Second Prince is extremely talented

6
00:01:23,685 --> 00:01:25,645
I just went to ask for some advice

7
00:01:27,025 --> 00:01:29,144
Then that's for private matters?

8
00:01:29,815 --> 00:01:30,475
Kind of

9
00:01:31,895 --> 00:01:33,645
The Second Prince has been married

10
00:01:34,145 --> 00:01:36,225
Our Southern Kingdom has always attached great importance to moral conduct

11
00:01:36,525 --> 00:01:38,225
It would be better if Your Highness could avoid suspicions

12
00:01:41,935 --> 00:01:43,895
It seems we have disturbed Her Highness's rest

13
00:01:43,895 --> 00:01:44,895
Let's go

14
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:49,144
By the way,

15
00:01:49,685 --> 00:01:52,525
there is something I want to remind you

16
00:01:54,105 --> 00:01:55,435
<i>Our</i> marriage

17
00:01:56,105 --> 00:01:57,605
is not decided by you

18
00:01:58,315 --> 00:02:00,145
or all the officials of the Southern Kingdom

19
00:02:01,435 --> 00:02:02,775
No one can decide

20
00:02:02,775 --> 00:02:04,225
my marriage

21
00:02:04,895 --> 00:02:07,015
I hope Your Highness doesn't go too far

22
00:02:08,145 --> 00:02:11,015
Otherwise, if our Southern Kingdom investigates the responsibility,

23
00:02:12,185 --> 00:02:13,855
it will not be affordable

24
00:02:13,855 --> 00:02:15,565
for you, a Princess

25
00:02:16,015 --> 00:02:16,564
Yes

26
00:02:17,395 --> 00:02:18,565
It's me who go too far

27
00:02:31,275 --> 00:02:32,104
Let's talk

28
00:02:32,685 --> 00:02:33,475
No need

29
00:02:34,275 --> 00:02:35,144
It seems my darling

30
00:02:35,815 --> 00:02:37,065
can solve it herself

31
00:02:38,775 --> 00:02:40,225
Your darling?

32
00:02:46,525 --> 00:02:47,685
You should practice horse riding and archery well

33
00:02:48,565 --> 00:02:49,565
Got it, Daddy

34
00:02:50,185 --> 00:02:50,895
Daddy

35
00:02:50,895 --> 00:02:52,015
My sister is a girl

36
00:02:52,185 --> 00:02:53,895
Shouldn't she practice needlework in the house?

37
00:02:54,685 --> 00:02:55,605
Her Majesty said

38
00:02:56,025 --> 00:02:58,144
women can also follow the Empress to defend the country

39
00:02:58,475 --> 00:02:59,775
So you have to practice well

40
00:02:59,935 --> 00:03:01,645
Otherwise, you will be left behind by your sister

41
00:03:03,895 --> 00:03:05,315
How about those ministers?

42
00:03:05,645 --> 00:03:07,025
Some couldn't stand it and went back

43
00:03:07,025 --> 00:03:07,935
But most of them

44
00:03:07,935 --> 00:03:09,225
were dragged out by their wives

45
00:03:09,225 --> 00:03:09,975
by the ears

46
00:03:09,975 --> 00:03:10,855
Horrible

47
00:03:11,225 --> 00:03:11,855
Good

48
00:03:12,105 --> 00:03:13,645
Looks like they'll be quiet for a few days

49
00:03:13,685 --> 00:03:14,725
Hong Dou

50
00:03:15,435 --> 00:03:16,225
Hong Dou

51
00:03:16,565 --> 00:03:17,065
Hong

52
00:03:20,435 --> 00:03:21,475
You can leave now

53
00:03:28,065 --> 00:03:30,475
The sun is shining brightly today

54
00:03:30,895 --> 00:03:31,815
My love to you

55
00:03:32,225 --> 00:03:32,975
is full

56
00:03:32,975 --> 00:03:35,225
Prince, why do you love <i>Us</i>?

57
00:03:37,275 --> 00:03:37,854
Um

58
00:03:39,275 --> 00:03:40,475
You are very beautiful

59
00:03:40,895 --> 00:03:42,145
and you're the Empress

60
00:03:42,725 --> 00:03:44,015
No one is better than you

61
00:03:44,355 --> 00:03:45,025
So are

62
00:03:46,065 --> 00:03:47,275
you willing to die for <i>Us</i>?

63
00:03:56,225 --> 00:03:57,105
I am afraid of the pain

64
00:04:40,775 --> 00:04:43,685
Your Majesty, why do you have to scare my brother like this?

65
00:04:47,315 --> 00:04:49,525
It seems that you two like this place very much

66
00:04:49,935 --> 00:04:51,935
It would be better for you to marry into the Southern Kingdom

67
00:04:51,935 --> 00:04:53,025
as a marriage alliance

68
00:04:53,475 --> 00:04:55,064
It's not impossible

69
00:04:56,145 --> 00:04:58,525
Princess, which of my brothers do you like?

70
00:05:00,935 --> 00:05:02,685
Ye Nanchen

71
00:05:05,435 --> 00:05:06,525
He's just a male concubine

72
00:05:07,435 --> 00:05:08,315
I do not care

73
00:05:09,065 --> 00:05:10,975
As long as we are in love

74
00:05:11,315 --> 00:05:12,975
How come you two are in love with each other?

75
00:05:13,895 --> 00:05:16,145
Didn't Your Majesty see it all that day?

76
00:05:22,775 --> 00:05:26,185
The Empress, by the Grace of Heaven, decreed that

77
00:05:26,475 --> 00:05:29,025
Ye Nanchen has good character

78
00:05:29,275 --> 00:05:30,775
and pretty looks,

79
00:05:31,105 --> 00:05:32,565
and is talented and knowledgeable

80
00:05:33,015 --> 00:05:35,854
He is very much loved by the Princess of the Northern Kingdom

81
00:05:35,935 --> 00:05:39,855
Now <i>We</i> specially name him as Prince Happy

82
00:05:40,065 --> 00:05:41,935
and bestow him a grand mansion,

83
00:05:41,935 --> 00:05:43,645
hundred acres of fertile land,

84
00:05:44,065 --> 00:05:46,025
and 10,000 teals of gold

85
00:05:46,275 --> 00:05:51,975
He shall marry the Princess of the Northern Kingdom on a designated day

86
00:05:54,275 --> 00:05:57,015
Mr. Ye, please accept the imperial edict

87
00:05:59,065 --> 00:06:00,275
Thanks to Her Majesty

88
00:06:02,065 --> 00:06:04,275
Mr. Ye, Her Majesty wishes you

89
00:06:05,145 --> 00:06:06,065
to be happy and have no worries

90
00:06:08,275 --> 00:06:09,064
Xue Wuming

91
00:06:09,065 --> 00:06:11,475
You... Call him Lord Xue. Eunuch Ai

92
00:06:20,895 --> 00:06:23,775
Chen, the Princess of the Northern Kingdom is a princess

93
00:06:23,775 --> 00:06:25,314
After all, she is a foreigner

94
00:06:25,525 --> 00:06:27,144
Then you two will have a little mixed-blood baby

95
00:06:27,355 --> 00:06:28,685
It's better than staying in this Cold Palace

96
00:06:28,815 --> 00:06:29,775
Oh, come on

97
00:06:29,815 --> 00:06:30,935
Look at his face,

98
00:06:30,935 --> 00:06:32,275
a reluctant look

99
00:06:32,275 --> 00:06:33,025
If I say,

100
00:06:33,145 --> 00:06:34,275
we two should go

101
00:06:34,475 --> 00:06:35,185
I think it's OK

102
00:06:41,315 --> 00:06:42,105
Give it back to <i>Us</i>

103
00:06:42,645 --> 00:06:44,315
Your Majesty, why should you care about a bean?

104
00:06:46,065 --> 00:06:46,975
Ye Nanchen

105
00:06:46,975 --> 00:06:48,605
You still know my name is Ye Nanchen

106
00:06:51,105 --> 00:06:52,645
Aren't you supposed to stay at the Cold Palace?

107
00:06:55,475 --> 00:06:56,895
You want me to marry another woman?

108
00:06:57,895 --> 00:06:59,605
Aren't you two in love?

109
00:07:01,105 --> 00:07:02,435
Do you have a heart?

110
00:07:03,475 --> 00:07:04,685
It's just perfect for you

111
00:07:05,275 --> 00:07:08,015
I died and came back to life, traveling through thousands of years to the Southern Kingdom

112
00:07:08,685 --> 00:07:10,645
Why do you keep pretending not to know me?

113
00:07:11,685 --> 00:07:12,225
<i>We</i>

114
00:07:12,815 --> 00:07:14,025
<i>We</i>...Although you're an Empress,

115
00:07:14,935 --> 00:07:16,645
you can't play with others' feelings at will

116
00:07:17,775 --> 00:07:19,025
Everything that is happening now

117
00:07:19,225 --> 00:07:20,935
is all because you can't help yourself time and time again

118
00:07:27,975 --> 00:07:29,064
Why don't you dare look at me?

119
00:07:35,275 --> 00:07:36,144
You and <i>We</i>

120
00:07:37,475 --> 00:07:39,105
are from two different worlds after all

121
00:07:42,225 --> 00:07:43,395
I'm standing right in front of you

122
00:07:43,525 --> 00:07:44,775
But <i>We</i>'re the Empress

123
00:07:44,775 --> 00:07:45,475
So what?
